{"status":200,"code":1000,"message":null,"timestamp":"1762171761103","path":null,"data":{"id":1428,"title":"FTLife:危疾及醫療計劃非標準保費推廣","type":"PRODUCT_PROMOTION","time":1669868139744,"tags":["富通保險"],"content":"<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">致合作夥伴：</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: #000000;\">為協助業務夥伴發展更多新生意業務，<strong>富通</strong>推出一個特別</span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">適用於危疾及健康產品的</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">非標準保費推廣計劃</span></strong>。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span></span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">受保人因健康理由<strong><span style=\"color: #236fa1;\">保費需調</span></strong></span><strong style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"color: #236fa1;\">高加幅至25%</span></strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\">，公司將以標準保費接受該保險申請，<strong>但</strong></span><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">需符合以下條件：</span></strong><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><strong>&nbsp;</strong> &nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #ba372a;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=\"color: #000000;\">1）</span>推廣期：2022年11月1日-2023年1月31日(包括在內)</span></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <strong>2）</strong></span></span><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">加幅25%保費的豁免不適用於曾患有或現正患有以下指定疾病的受保人：<strong><span style=\"color: #236fa1;\">乙型肝炎/乙型肝炎帶菌者或丙型肝炎/丙型肝炎帶菌者、癌症/冠狀動脈疾病/中風/糖尿病</span></strong>&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 3）合資格產品：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/INFORMATION/2022-12-01/94c6d5a7fb4845fd99d491f533e05970.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 詳情請參閱附件。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 1.5; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"> </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><!--EndFragment--></span></p>","attachments":[{"fileName":"Memo-TC.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2022-12-01/ca6ac81d1ecb42679a666724960ad22b.pdf","uploadTime":1669862076030,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null},{"fileName":"Memo-EN.pdf","filePath":"https://beefintech-centre.oss-accelerate.aliyuncs.com/COMMON/2022-12-01/ae2b1b8ff3f0493eb8ca67193a030b2d.pdf","uploadTime":1669862080149,"author":"BEEFINTECH-CENTRE","tags":null,"fileSize":null}],"companyCode":"FTLIFE","companyName":"周大福人壽","productCodes":["FTLIFE:TCCP","FTLIFE:HC168PCIP","FTLIFE:HECIP","FTLIFE:PSCIP","FTLIFE:MCMIP","FTLIFE:WCMIP","FTLIFE:BCMIP","FTLIFE:TCMIP","FTLIFE:FCMIP","FTLIFE:MESBP","FTLIFE:MEHCP","FTLIFE:METUMP","FTLIFE:MGPIP","FTLIFE:MSMA"],"productNames":["護痊保癌症保障計劃","守護168危疾保障計劃(加強版)","康健易危疾保障計劃","首護易危疾保障計劃","摯康健醫療保障計劃","卓康保醫療保障計劃","樂康保醫療保障計劃","摯康保醫療保障計劃","悅康保醫療保障計劃","樂康健手術保障計劃","樂康健住院現金保障計劃","樂康健升級醫療計劃","御醫保特級醫療